I've heard of a few different variations of this game, so I am not sure if I played it properly. In school we would play it with choosing a word such as "Apple" and then starting the next work with the last letter of the previous word, so "E" words. The way I chose to play was to type in a random word to start and just whatever I immediately thought of based off the first is what I would type next. I found this to be more enjoyable because it was right off the top of the brain.
